sa kanila, "Hindi ka nagkakamali,"

00:22:32.484 --> 00:22:34.353
habang nakikipaglaban sila na may hawak na baril.

00:22:37.723 --> 00:22:42.060
Kaya naman kailangang tapusin ang digmaan.

00:22:43.662 --> 00:22:45.364
Naiintindihan ko iyon.

00:22:46.231 --> 00:22:48.734
Ngunit hindi ganoon kadaling
alisin ang digmaan.

00:22:49.267 --> 00:22:50.535
